						</p>

						<p>
							<label for="message" id="lmessage">Message:</label>
							<textarea name="message" id="message" onfocus="input_focus('message');" onblur="input_blur('message');"></textarea>
						</p>
						<div class="x"></div>
						<p class="error" id="message-error">You must enter your message.</p>

						<p>
